    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Creating arrays\n",
        "\n",
        "### Arrays created from lists and other array-like objects\n"
      ],
      "id": "6841d34f"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array([1, 2, 3, 4])\n",
        "data.ndim, data.shape"
      ],
      "id": "5926462f",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array(((1, 2), (3, 4)))\n",
        "data.ndim, data.shape"
      ],
      "id": "261958c3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Arrays filled with constant values\n"
      ],
      "id": "629c478d"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.zeros((2, 3))"
      ],
      "id": "e76da974",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.ones(4)\n",
        "data, data.dtype"
      ],
      "id": "9ed4dbd1",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "5.4 * np.ones(10)"
      ],
      "id": "7e944ef8",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.full(10, 5.4) # slightly more efficient"
      ],
      "id": "de0de758",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x1 = np.empty(5)\n",
        "x1.fill(3.0)\n",
        "x1"
      ],
      "id": "34b77385",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Arrays filled with incremental sequences\n"
      ],
      "id": "32fb13aa"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.arange(0, 11, 1)"
      ],
      "id": "9c51814e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.linspace(0, 10, 11)  # generally recommended"
      ],
      "id": "1e3302e0",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Arrays filled with logarithmic sequences\n"
      ],
      "id": "ab2b9c4b"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.logspace(0, 2, 10)  # 5 data points between 10**0=1 to 10**2=100"
      ],
      "id": "cc9deffd",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Mesh grid arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "ef4e1405"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = np.array([-1, 0, 1])\n",
        "y = np.array([-2, 0, 2])\n",
        "\n",
        "X, Y = np.meshgrid(x, y)"
      ],
      "id": "0ac7b73d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "X"
      ],
      "id": "c5158997",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Y"
      ],
      "id": "3147d474",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Z = (X + Y)**2\n",
        "Z"
      ],
      "id": "c953fa86",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Creating uninitialized arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "45c84c32"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.empty(3, dtype=float)"
      ],
      "id": "84ab8142",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Creating arrays with properties of other arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "1eac649c"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "def f(x):    \n",
        "    y = np.ones_like(x)    # compute with x and y    \n",
        "    return y\n",
        "\n",
        "x = np.array([[1, 2, 3], [4, 5, 6]])\n",
        "y = f(x)\n",
        "y"
      ],
      "id": "5c35bd45",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Creating matrix arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "04a0ab02"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.identity(4)"
      ],
      "id": "4224f338",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.eye(4, k=1)"
      ],
      "id": "104a3230",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.eye(4, k=-1)"
      ],
      "id": "4dbb3c23",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.diag(np.arange(0, 20, 5))"
      ],
      "id": "a775a3fc",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Indexing and slicing\n",
        "\n",
        "### One-dimensional arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "ff3af789"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a = np.arange(0, 11)\n",
        "a"
      ],
      "id": "e038d674",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[0]"
      ],
      "id": "a7367918",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[-1]"
      ],
      "id": "b4d4aa10",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[4]"
      ],
      "id": "766b3ca4",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "5e41806f"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[1:-1]"
      ],
      "id": "b394f071",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[1:-1:2]"
      ],
      "id": "7a235480",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "eabc108f"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[:5]"
      ],
      "id": "4a32f7c0",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[-5:]"
      ],
      "id": "298724a1",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[::-2]"
      ],
      "id": "9b3f77e9",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Multidimensional arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "d622de73"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "f = lambda m, n: n + 10*m"
      ],
      "id": "2c6aaffd",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# please search for numpy.fromfunction at google\n",
        "A = np.fromfunction(f, (6, 6), dtype=int)\n",
        "A  "
      ],
      "id": "bc59c037",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[:, 1]  # the second column"
      ],
      "id": "3b92e278",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[1, :]  # the second row"
      ],
      "id": "b23b90d7",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[:3, :3]"
      ],
      "id": "0e113069",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[3:, :3]"
      ],
      "id": "64560850",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[::2, ::2]"
      ],
      "id": "1678c293",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[1::2, 1::3]"
      ],
      "id": "416d27ba",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Views\n",
        "\n",
        "* Subarrays that are extracted from arrays using slice operations are **alternative views** of the same underlying array data. That is, $~$they are arrays that refer to the same data in memory as the original array, $~$but with a different `strides` configuration\n",
        "\n",
        "* When elements in a view are assigned new values, $~$the values of the original\n",
        "array are therefore also updated. For example,\n"
      ],
      "id": "fc599b5c"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B = A[1:5, 1:5]\n",
        "B"
      ],
      "id": "b1433650",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B[:, :] = 0\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "5d8d4fd5",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "* When a copy rather than a view is needed, the view can be copied explicitly by using the `copy` method of the `ndarray` instance\n"
      ],
      "id": "2203156d"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "C = B[1:3, 1:3].copy()\n",
        "C"
      ],
      "id": "064c9422",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "C[:, :] = 1\n",
        "C"
      ],
      "id": "c00b33f9",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B"
      ],
      "id": "b060cbd7",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Fancy indexing and boolean-valued indexing\n"
      ],
      "id": "76fc626b"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.linspace(0, 1, 11)\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "767df9b3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[np.array([0, 2, 4])]"
      ],
      "id": "8a3d72b2",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[[0, 2, 4]]"
      ],
      "id": "7d32abd3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "dfaca87e"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A > 0.5"
      ],
      "id": "7c09d683",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[A > 0.5]"
      ],
      "id": "66acead3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "* Unlike arrays created by using slices, $~$**the arrays returned using fancy indexing and Boolean-valued\n",
        "indexing are not views**, $~$but rather new independent arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "b4c0b4dd"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(10)\n",
        "indices = [2, 4, 6]"
      ],
      "id": "5823cb49",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B = A[indices]"
      ],
      "id": "795fd0c7",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B[0] = -1\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "c8112c78",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[indices] = -1\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "a3dc8673",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "0017279b"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(10)"
      ],
      "id": "940dce82",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B = A[A > 5]"
      ],
      "id": "560de958",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B[0] = -1\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "38f591b0",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[A > 5] = -1\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "3edb014c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Summery\n"
      ],
      "id": "aecc09e0"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), ':, :')"
      ],
      "id": "a6780f96",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '0')"
      ],
      "id": "35e8fde1",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '1, :')"
      ],
      "id": "5d962fff",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), ':, 2')"
      ],
      "id": "d545bc47",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "da6240e5"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '0:2, 0:2')"
      ],
      "id": "42f301bb",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '0:2, 2:4')"
      ],
      "id": "49996515",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '::2, ::2')"
      ],
      "id": "d8259cc3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '1::2, 1::2')"
      ],
      "id": "15e73bab",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), ':, [0, 3]')"
      ],
      "id": "3fac92be",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '[1, 3], [0, 3]')"
      ],
      "id": "b78cc11a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), ':, [False, True, True, False]')"
      ],
      "id": "4d301298",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '1:3, [False, True, True, False]')"
      ],
      "id": "c9ade59e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Reshaping and resizing\n",
        "\n",
        "* Reshaping an array does not require modifying the underlying array data; it only changes in how the data is interpreted, by redefining the array’s strides attribute\n"
      ],
      "id": "1350a7f8"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array([[1, 2], [3, 4]])\n",
        "data1 = np.reshape(data, (1, 4))\n",
        "data1"
      ],
      "id": "f652490b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data1[0, 1] = -1\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "14e7b9f3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2 = data.reshape(4)\n",
        "data2"
      ],
      "id": "50165632",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2[1] = -2\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "33960217",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "825de661"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array([[1, 2], [3, 4]])\n",
        "data1 = np.ravel(data)\n",
        "data1"
      ],
      "id": "969a73cc",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data1[0] = -1\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "051a3fb0",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "* The `ndarray` method `flatten` perform the same function, $~$but\n",
        "returns a **copy** instead of a view\n"
      ],
      "id": "18793f59"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2 = data.flatten()\n",
        "data2"
      ],
      "id": "872fa1b8",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2[0] = -2\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "46f661cd",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "7ec47972"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.arange(0, 5)\n",
        "data.shape"
      ],
      "id": "cb731988",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "column = data[:, np.newaxis]\n",
        "column"
      ],
      "id": "4ab9eff5",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "column.shape"
      ],
      "id": "b814e986",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "row = data[np.newaxis, :]\n",
        "row"
      ],
      "id": "d005834b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "row.shape"
      ],
      "id": "bb5f2483",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "row[0, 0] = -1\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "d1fab5c6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
